  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      The investigators designed a study to determine whether Propofol or Sevoflurane would provide
      same postoperative sleep quality in patients undergoing thyroidectomy.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
  <detailed_description>
    <textblock>
      The investigators designed a study to determine whether Propofol or Sevoflurane would provide
      same postoperative sleep quality in patients undergoing thyroidectomy.The bispectral index
      score (BIS) was monitored during the operation and the first postoperative night.
    </textblock>
  </detailed_description>
